{"ts": "2026-06-07T20:16:12.205890+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 0ae7697cb0b8b826a72bd1bf30a3475783001b69)", "id": "lc_c7324c5b-1126-4024-9470-373bb3edf0dc"}, {"type": "text", "text": "# Build setup\n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- Flutter SDK 3.22 or newer (`flutter --version`)\n- Dart 3.4+\n- For web: `flutter config --enable-web`\n- For Android: Android Studio with `cmdline-tools;latest` installed\n\n## Common commands\n\n```bash\nflutter pub get\nflutter run -d chrome           # local dev for web\nflutter build web --release     # release artifacts under build/web/\nflutter build apk --release     # Android APK\n```\n\n## Finnkino API\n\nThe app fetches showtimes from `https://www.finnkino.fi/xml/Schedule` — a public\nXML feed; no API key required.\n", "id": "lc_9f2c0267-34e4-44b9-9bb6-a13a7ccee657"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "e65bdf43-a244-4745-bdbb-36b97a77f981", "tool_call_id": "call_00_SdQTe8QUcYoMCj64zPzh5016", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
